<paragraph blockId="7.[151,549,257,282]" box="[151,549,257,282]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">
<taxonomicName authority="Mulsant" authorityName="Mulsant" authorityYear="1858" box="[151,450,257,282]" class="Insecta" family="Oedemeridae" genus="Asclera" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="548" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="xanthoderes">
<emphasis box="[151,358,258,282]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">Asclera xanthoderes</emphasis>
Mulsant
</taxonomicName>
, 188: 232
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,328,607]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,301,328,354]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">New records</emphasis>
. The numerous new records we examined from 
<collectingCountry box="[845,909,328,354]" name="Spain" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">Spain</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[963,1058,328,354]" name="Portugal" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">Portugal</collectingCountry>
were included in a map available online (https://www.iucnredlist.org/species/86859903/87312604#geographic-range).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,328,607]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">
The species was described by Mulsant (1858) based on two specimens, one from Var Department (afterwards probably considered as type locality) and another from Sicily, which actually refers to the 
<taxonomicName authority="Bologna &amp; Poloni &amp; Vázquez, 2019" authorityName="Bologna &amp; Poloni &amp; Vázquez" authorityYear="2019" box="[1152,1242,436,462]" class="Insecta" family="Oedemeridae" genus="Ischnomera" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="548" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sicula" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[1152,1242,436,462]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">I. sicula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1248,1307,437,463]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
This specimen, not examined by us, could be selected as 
<typeStatus box="[692,795,472,498]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">lectotype</typeStatus>
after ist examination, now not possible. Several records from the Iberian Peninsula and southern 
<collectingCountry box="[600,676,509,535]" name="France" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">France</collectingCountry>
were published (e.g 
<bibRefCitation author="Mulsant, E." box="[906,1070,507,534]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548" refId="ref5727" refString="Mulsant, E. (1857) Coleopteres de France, Vesicants. Magnin, Blanchard et Cie, Paris, 201 pp." type="book" year="1857">Mulsant, 1857</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Pic, M." box="[1081,1188,508,534]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548" pagination="11 - 13" refId="ref5751" refString="Pic, M. (1898) Notes sur divers Coleopteres. Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de France, 1898, 11 - 13." type="journal article" year="1898">Pic, 1898</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Mayet, V." box="[1199,1342,508,535]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548" pagination="33 - 40" refId="ref5695" refString="Mayet, V. (1903) Contribution a la faune entomologique des Pyrenees orientales-Coleopteres. Coleopteres des Alberes (suite). Miscellanea Entomologica, 11, 33 - 40." type="journal article" year="1903">Mayet, 1903</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Caillol, H." pageId="7" pageNumber="548" refId="ref5350" refString="Caillol, H. (1919) Catalogue des Coleopteres de Provence, d'apres des documents recueilles et groupes. 3 eme Partie. Memoires de la Societe Linneenne de Provence, Marseille, 594 pp." type="book" year="1919">Caillol, 1919</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Magistretti, M." box="[223,420,544,570]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548" pagination="5 - 20" refId="ref5635" refString="Magistretti, M. (1942) Contributo alla conoscenza degli Oedemeridi paleartici V. Gli Oedemeridi della collezione Dodero. Memorie della Societa entomologica italiana, 21, 5 - 20." type="journal article" year="1942">Magistretti, 1942</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Allemand, R." box="[431,616,543,570]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548" pagination="137 - 142" refId="ref5167" refString="Allemand, R. (1995) Identification et repartition des especes francaises d' Ischnomera (Coleoptera Oedemeridae). Bulletin mensuel de la Societe Linneenne de Lyon, 64, 137 - 142. https: // doi. org / 10.3406 / linly. 1995.11064" type="journal article" year="1995">Allemand, 1995</bibRefCitation>
; Vázquez, 2002; 
<bibRefCitation author="Lopez-Perez, J. &amp; Vazquez, X. A." box="[813,1166,544,571]" pageId="7" pageNumber="548" pagination="48 - 49" refId="ref5545" refString="Lopez-Perez, J. &amp; Vazquez, X. A. (2016) Presencia de Ischnomera xanthoderes (Mulsant, 1858) (Coleoptera: Oedemeridae) en la provincia de Huelva (Suroeste de Andalucia, Espana). Boletin de la Sociedad Andaluza de Entomologia, 26, 48 - 49." type="journal article" year="2016">López-Pérez &amp; Vázquez, 2016</bibRefCitation>
). 
<figureCitation box="[1186,1252,544,570]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="7.[151,203,1612,1639]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,626,1587]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1436,626,1587]" captionText="FIG. 8. Distribution of the species of the Ischnomera xanthoderes complex: I. xanthoderes, light blue spot; I. tenietensis, green; I. sicula n. sp., red." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3469734" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3469734/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="548">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
